Rating: 4
wonderful recipe! even my 14 yr old son, who doesn't like bread pudding loved this with cinnamon caramel sauce: 1/4 cup cream, 1/2 cup (packed) golden brown sugar, 1/8 teaspoon (generous) ground cinnamon, 1 teaspoons vanilla extract. Combine brown sugar and 1/4 cup cream in small saucepan. Stir over medium heat until sugar dissolves and caramel sauce is smooth. Remove from heat; stir in cinnamon and vanilla.

